title: Franz Ferdinand – No You Girls (live for The Current)
description:
In March of 2022, Franz Ferdinand released the double-album set, 'Hits To The Head,' which features 18 hits from the band’s back catalogue as well as two new tracks. While Franz Ferdinand were on tour to promote the double album, they visited The Current studio to perform three tracks from the collection, including this song, “No You Girls” (originally on 2009’s 'Tonight: Franz Ferdinand' album). 

Band members
Alex Kapranos – guitar, vocals
Audrey Tait – drums
Bob Hardy – bass
Dino Bardot – guitar
Julian Corrie – keyboards, guitar

Credits
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Camera Operators – Evan Clark, Derek Ramirez
Audio – Eric Xu Romani
Video – Evan Clark
Digital Producer – Luke Taylor

title: MUNA discuss their self-titled album (interview at The Current)
description:
MUNA, now signed to Phoebe Bridgers' label Saddest Factory Records, recently visited The Current studio to play acoustic versions of songs from their new self-titled album and to talk with host Jade. Watch the complete interview above. 

See three-song studio performance: 

Band members
Catherine "Katie" Gavin
Naomi McPherson
Josette Maskin
